--- SMD_TS1_TS3 ---

Steered MD stage generating the starting configurations for the TS1 <-> TS3 umbrella-sampling
scan (see ../USW_100_TS1_TS3/README and ../README). Driven along 'cowh' (COORDINATION of the
nucleophilic water/oxygen with the surrounding hydrogens — tracks the nucleophile's hydration
reorganization between the two stationary points): MOVINGRESTRAINT pulls cowh from AT0=0.9 to
AT1=2.1 over 100000 steps, KAPPA=200 kcal/mol/A^2, under the same background wall restraints
as the other pph4 pipelines (see PMF_react_TS1/SMD_react_TS1/README). Restart snapshots are
converted into 'lmp_files/' seed structures the same way.

rep2 additionally has a 'safe/' subfolder — a backup copy of an earlier state of that
replica's run (same file set as the top level); rep1 and rep3 have no equivalent.

Three replicas (rep1/2/3) — one README covers all three.

Note: this README documents pre-existing content; no existing file was modified.
